# Spec Driven Workflow

- Read `docs/specs/00-index.md` before planning or implementing.
- Use `docs/agent-guides/spec-workflow.md` to choose only relevant specs.
- Treat specs as source of truth.
- Treat `docs/memory` as temporary notes only.
- If a decision becomes stable, promote it from memory to the responsible spec.
- Do not load all specs by default; select 2 to 4 relevant specs.
- Keep `docs/specs/process/13-readme-entrega.md` for final delivery documentation.
